channel.title: People can join my server =/
channel.description:
Ok i made a server using Testscape. to start my server i do this, open no-ip make sure jiescape.no-ip.biz is checked with rosey cheeks, compile the server, run server. i open up moparscapeDOTorg click new server and type in jiescape.no-ip.biz and new port 43594. hit start server, it says unable to startup-port already in use? and then i hit enter and sign in. something is wrong.
Any ideas, Thanks in advance, Michael [br][br][size=1]Posted on: December 02, 2007, 02:59:06 PM[/size][hr]update, i went downstairs and tryed signing in, it worked! but it wouldnt load, it hung at loading... please wait.
